{"title":"Canyon’s best-selling bike now available in the US, it’s the Grand Canyon hardtail mountain bike","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/07/15/canyons-best-selling-bike-now-available-in-the-us-its-the-grand-canyon-hardtail-mountain-bike/","date":1626389577000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p>The Canyon Grand Canyon hardtail mountain bike has been their best selling bike in Europe, and now it’s stateside with a $1,299 price tag. Well, it’s just one model from that line, but it’s solid entry level offering with full SRAM drivetrain, Shimano brakes, and a Rockshox fork. There’s even a dropper seatpost…</p><h3>2021 Grand Canyon hardtail specs</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15184913/2021-canyon-grand-canyon-hardtail-mountain-bike-for-us-1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15184913/2021-canyon-grand-canyon-hardtail-mountain-bike-for-us-1.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x268/rscb25/ng:webp/ngcb25\" alt=\"2021 canyon grand canyon hardtail mountain bike studio photo\" width=\"1118\" height=\"618\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15184913/2021-canyon-grand-canyon-hardtail-mountain-bike-for-us-1.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb25 1118w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15184913/2021-canyon-grand-canyon-hardtail-mountain-bike-for-us-1-297x164.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb25 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15184913/2021-canyon-grand-canyon-hardtail-mountain-bike-for-us-1-800x442.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb25 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15184913/2021-canyon-grand-canyon-hardtail-mountain-bike-for-us-1-120x66.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb25 120w,https://b